name: B&M 70503 Cast Aluminum Differential Cover for GM 8.2" 10 Bolt B.O.P.
shortDescription:
Compatible with GM 8.2 in. 10-bolt (Buick Olds, Pontiac) Differential cover;

Our engineers designed the line of Hi-Tek differential covers to not only look good but address a number of weaknesses of the factory stamped steel covers. First, they started by constructing the covers of thick A356.0-T6 aluminum, which dissipates heat much faster than the factory steel unit keeping the fluid temperature lower under high-stress loads vs. a steel cover. Then for added durability, we added a reinforced center bar for extra strength along with load bolts to help prevent bearing cap deflection under severe loads. The internal shape of the cover retains the smooth round back internally to help keep the fluid flow going over the ring gear to properly lubricate the gears and bearings. Additional features include a magnetic drain plug for catching ferrous metal particles, machined B&M logo and all necessary hardware and easy to follow detailed instructions for a quick and simple installation you can do at home. Note: Gasket not Included;

name: Dump Truck Pinata - Kids Construction Birthday Party Supplies, Construction Party Decorations (Small, 15.5x9x6 In)
shortDescription:
Item Description

Bring the excitement of a construction site to your child's birthday celebration with this small pinata, a great way to check "construction pinata" off your construction birthday party supplies list. This construction-themed party essential is designed to ignite the imaginations of little builders and add a touch of adventure to any construction themed birthday party. Our dump truck pinata features a vibrant yellow body that captures the essence of a real top-loading dump truck. The striking orange bin on top adds a delightful pop of color, creating a visually appealing centerpiece for your celebration. This pinata's design is further enhanced by the inclusion of realistic details such as white windows, black tires, and yellow wheels, bringing the construction theme to life. This pinata offers a serious amount of fun for kids; simply fill it with an assortment of candies, toys, or small surprises, and watch as the children eagerly await their turn to reveal what's inside. This pinata measures 15.5x9x6 and is designed with an easy-to-use hanging loop, allowing you to effortlessly suspend it from a sturdy support. When the time comes, simply let the little builders take turns at striking the pinata with a safe, soft bat until it bursts open, revealing the hidden debris for all to clean up on the job site.
